- 'Re-evaluation' typically refers to follow-up examinations to assess changes in the patient's condition;
- 'Diet and Periodontal Health' is a research study investigating the relationship between dietary habits and periodontal health.

sql:
SELECT AVG(num_conditions)
FROM (
  SELECT patient_id, COUNT(DISTINCT medical_condition) as num_conditions
  FROM medical_history
  GROUP BY patient_id
);

